@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xcgpwx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.68) * tmp) / ((v0 + 0.10 * v2 + 0.88) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.49)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v0 + 0.59 / v2 + 0.05)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.60 - v2 + 0.53)) + (wp.abs(v1 + 0.00) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.99)))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.64)))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = wp.abs(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
